dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Milwaukee_Addresses_YE2016.[points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which the address is associated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which the address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed per parcel or building ]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
